name: Autumn Game Jam - Leaf Leap
description:
Play as a girl named Katie who loves rollerblading through her COZY street during brisk autumn afternoons.

Leap over obstacles in your path, to keep your speed as you leap off the ramp and into a giant pile of leaves!

Created over 10 working days as a part of the 2022 Autumn Game Jam. 

The Team: 
Project Lead - Andrew Hickin.

Game Designer Bekki Broughton.

Programming- Chris Bjoerk.

Audio - SFX and Balancing - Ronal Kitcher-Pentey.

Music Composer- Victor Lim. 

Player Character by Michael Sampaio Via Sketch Fab.
